author: rhuijben
msg: (force_del_tc_inside): In WC-NG on an incoming delete, local edit tree
conflict we copy the base tree and remove BASE. The delete will therefore
result in removing the now added nodes.
Philip recently made svn rm --force remove tree conflicts while deleting.
After updating the expected result I could remove the XFail marking.
